That is not enough. You need also the include path of RcppArmadillo in 
the PKG_CXXFLAGS

system.file( "include", package = "RcppArmadillo" )

and you need additional libraries in your PKG_LIBS:

$(LAPACK_LIBS) $(BLAS_LIBS) $(FLIBS)

All of this is written in clear text in both sources of documentation.

